SUMMARY:Online Meetup
DESCRIPTION:We’re meeting on Discord! The link to join the Baltimore Indie Game Devs discord server will be in your Meetup RSVP message. \nJoin us to discuss game development\, talk shop\, and bounce ideas. Anyone with an interest in game design and development is welcome\, from beginners to veteran professionals. \nIf you’re working on a game\, you’re welcome to show it and ask for feedback. There will be plenty of time to chat and talk shop\, too.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/online-meetup-7/
END:VEVENT
