LAST-MODIFIED:20251123T204845Z
UID:369-1766221200-1766343600@baltimoreindiegames.com
SUMMARY:Dig Dug Dig Market & Festival
DESCRIPTION:Location: Northeast D.C. at multiple venues including metrobar\, City State Brewing\, Lost Generation Brewing Company\, and Bryant St. Market. \nDetails: D.C.’s newest and biggest holiday market\, featuring vendors\, a “Winter Wonderland” theme at some locations\, a dog fashion show\, cookie exchanges and contests\, gift wrapping stations\, and indie video game showcases. \nAdmission: The event is free to attend. \nSaturday\, Dec 20\, 2025\nParade 9am\nDoors at 11am\nFestival end times vary from venue to venue \nSunday\, Dec 21\, 2025\nDoors at 11am\nFestival ends at 7pm \nGame Submission Form: If you’re an indie dev and you’d like to show your game\, please complete the Submission Form.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/dig-dug-dig-market-festival/
END:VEVENT
